{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/vim-coc-tabnine-autocomplete/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Code Me, dsewnr","author":"dsewnr"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6d1b3333-5bb0-5dda-9dfa-815a2c9dc0b4","excerpt":"原本對 TabNine 是持保留態度，好像沒有也沒差… 今天在做手工的時候終於發現它的好處了…  如圖，TabNine 已經學習到我今天的做的事了… (自動幫我加上 prefix) 雖然是免費版的，但也讓我少做了不少手工！超爽的！ 推薦給各位我使用的 Vim plugins: coc.nvim、coc-tabnine…","html":"<p>原本對 <a href=\"https://tabnine.com/\">TabNine</a> 是持保留態度，好像沒有也沒差…</p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>今天在做手工的時候終於發現它的好處了…</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"vim coc tabnine\"\n        title=\"vim coc tabnine\"\n        src=\"/static/dfc2c0e1afac533813ee8c668b8742d5/80e3c/vim-coc-tabnine.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dfc2c0e1afac533813ee8c668b8742d5/4ec73/vim-coc-tabnine.jpg 180w,\n/static/dfc2c0e1afac533813ee8c668b8742d5/158ba/vim-coc-tabnine.jpg 360w,\n/static/dfc2c0e1afac533813ee8c668b8742d5/80e3c/vim-coc-tabnine.jpg 720w,\n/static/dfc2c0e1afac533813ee8c668b8742d5/47311/vim-coc-tabnine.jpg 1080w,\n/static/dfc2c0e1afac533813ee8c668b8742d5/ff224/vim-coc-tabnine.jpg 1085w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>如圖，TabNine 已經學習到我今天的做的事了… (自動幫我加上 prefix)</p>\n<p>雖然是免費版的，但也讓我少做了不少手工！超爽的！</p>\n<p>推薦給各位我使用的 Vim plugins: <a href=\"https://github.com/neoclide/coc.nvim\">coc.nvim</a>、<a href=\"https://github.com/neoclide/coc-tabnine\">coc-tabnine</a>。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>在 TabNine 網站上申請了 <a href=\"https://tabnine.com/beta_signup\">TabNine Beta 試用</a>，馬上就收到試用的邀請！</p>\n<p>原本一直在 Vim command 裡面找 TabNine::config，試了老久都找不到…</p>\n<p>後來才發現要直接打在內容裡… XD 打完就會跳出輸入 token 的頁面了！(果然是很 AI)</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Vim TabNine Autocomplete","date":"August 15, 2019"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/vim-coc-tabnine-autocomplete/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/golang-mongodb-mgo-v2-unmaintained/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"gopkg.in/mgo.v2 Is Unmaintained"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/coscup-2019/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"COSCUP 2019"}}}}}